CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 21, 1956, pg. A2, reads: "First Communion - Marie Therese, 8, and Carol Ann, 7, daughters of Mr. and Mrs. Warren Oliver, of Rankin, took their first communion last Sunday at St. Brendan Roman Catholic Church, Braddock, with the Rev. Father Bernard L. Berg officiating. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Marie Therese Oliver and Carol Ann Oliver wearing first communion dresses and veils, holding small prayer books and standing on area rug in St. Brendan Catholic Church, Braddock
